=head2 0.52 2006-03-12

=over

=item added some dependencies to F<Build.PL>/F<META.yml> (thanks to
L<Achim Grolms|https://metacpan.org/author/agrolms> and
L<BLBLACK|https://metacpan.org/author/blblack>
